: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"1a91f325537c342953d061c3786e7ac4c4b190a4","tid":1611473,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWYmKi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWYmKi5.jpg&h=ca400a93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyJBycr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyJBycr.jpg&h=9fe3c8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4Z88LM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4Z88LM.jpg&h=fdc8f569&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cbd59a7008c7bb8b17eb5a21238f9cd852b23ea","tid":1611473,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"有位巴打講得岩 中共無可能會授意係生日會開槍殺人<br />\n根本依家黑狗由上至下都已經全盤失控 不受控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376cf9dd54cd0dda563f56d1597dceea66daaaa2","tid":1611473,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"10月5日，香港民族抗爭運動，由五大轉到反共？<br />\n<br />\n10月6日，星期日罷買日，今個星期輪到邊個商場？<br />\n<br />\n10月9日，抗爭四個月，天琦上訴案<br />\n<br />\n10月10，中華民國國慶<br />\n<br />\n10月12，6.12第一槍四個月"}]}